99
00:12:25,489 --> 00:12:28,220
Nisam je morao kupovati.

100
00:12:28,260 --> 00:12:33,136
Lik po imenu Tad, uzgaja travu
i ima dozvolu. Legalno je.

101
00:12:33,637 --> 00:12:38,035
Uzeli smo samo malo, jer
smo željeli probati. -U redu,

102
00:12:38,036 --> 00:12:42,055
